# Keep the build context small and reproducible. The production images
# (infra/production/*.Dockerfile) install dependencies from the committed
# lockfile inside the builder stage, so no host node_modules or build output
# should ever be sent to the daemon.
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.venv
ai/.venv
**/*.tsbuildinfo

.git
.github
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Docs and local-only artifacts are never needed to build a runnable image.
docs
*.md
!packages/**/README.md
.data
backups
scratchpad

# Test/coverage output
coverage
**/coverage
**/*.log
